Interface PsiJavaCodeReferenceElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Iconable, PsiElement, PsiJavaReference, PsiPolyVariantReference, PsiQualifiedReference, PsiQualifiedReferenceElement, PsiReference, PsiSymbolReference, SymbolReference, UserDataHolder
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    PsiAnnotatedJavaCodeReferenceElement, PsiImportStaticReferenceElement, PsiMethodReferenceExpression, PsiReferenceExpression
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ClsJavaCodeReferenceElementImpl, ClsReferenceExpressionImpl, LightClassReference, LightClassReferenceExpression, LightClassTypeReference, LightMemberReference, LightPackageReference, LightPackageReferenceExpression, PsiImportStaticReferenceElementImpl, PsiJavaCodeReferenceElementImpl, PsiMethodReferenceExpressionImpl, PsiReferenceExpressionImpl

    public interface PsiJavaCodeReferenceElement
extends PsiJavaReference, PsiQualifiedReferenceElement
    Represents a reference found in Java code (either an identifier or a sequence of identifiers separated by periods, optionally with generic type arguments).
